<p class="lh-copy measure center">Mike returns to the winery, working 3 days a week. Kristina graduates from High School. We have our biggest set back ever as Jennifer passes away.</p>

<p class="bg-light-silver lh-copy measure center">Mike returns to help out at the winery the first order of business, building a new crush pad. Jenny passes away. Kristina graduates H.S.</p>

<h3 class="mt4">2001</h3>
<p class="lh-copy measure center">Randy makes the first vintage of the Palmaz wine here, as they construct their facility. Lori passes her exam and becomes a Master Gardner. Planted the Lake Vineyard and purchased the New Hearth property.</p>
<p class="lh-copy measure center">Adan Salgado is hired on full time to assist in the vineyard not only is he still a part of the team, but is responsible for waxing the Howell Mountain wine every vintage.</p>

<h3 class="mt4">2003</h3>
<p class="lh-copy measure center">Randy makes the first vintage of Feather for the Long Shadows project in the Columbia Valley of Washington. Mike buys the old vine Petite Sirah from Randy’s Park Muscatine Vineyard and starts the Retro Cellars label with Kara. </p>

<h3 class="mt4">2004</h3>
