<h3 class="mt4">2005</h3>
<p class="lh-copy measure center">Kristina graduates from Cal Poly. The first class of their Wine and Viticulture program. </p>
<p class="lh-copy measure center">Rosalio Olivera is hired full time to assist in the vineyard and remains a valuable member of the team today.</p>

